15 WHEREAS, Reign Over Cancer Inc. has had a tremendous impact on its community through
16 its spirit of service and commitment to improving the quality of life in the State of Georgia;
17 and
18 WHEREAS, Reign Stevens has long been dedicated to providing unparalleled service and
19 support, and she remains steadfastly committed to the principles of skill, integrity, and
20 responsibility; and
21 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the outstanding accomplishments of this
22 extraordinary organization be appropriately recognized.
23 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
24 the members of this body commend Reign Over Cancer Inc. for its many exemplary
25 contributions to the citizens of this state and extend best wishes for its continued success.
26 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
27 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Reign
28 Over Cancer Inc.
